Task 2:
Implement an algorithm for making a simple calculator with all the operators (+, -,*,/%):

•	Start 
•	Ask user to input Two number
•	Ask user to input operator (+,-,*,/,%)
•	If user input “+” add both numbers
•	Print the Result
•	If user input “-” Subtract first from second number
•	Print the Result
•	If user input “*” Multiply both numbers
•	Print the Result
•	If user input “/” Divide first from second number
•	Print the Result
•	If user input “%” Divide first from second number
•	Print the Result (Remainder)
•	End
